{"tid":2317264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"身負7條控罪拒絕流亡 尹兆堅：絕不退出民主運動","createTime":"2020-12-08T12:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T13:24:03.000Z","uid":212249,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"e0d15a23ac34970e9d0c28340cc18ff69c394560","tid":2317264,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:02:06.000Z","msg":"尹兆堅辭去立法會議員職務後，繼續擔任區議員及民主黨中委，沒有退出政壇的打算。多次遭受警暴、身兼7條控罪的他說，沒有想過流亡，自己一定會繼續留在香港參與民主運動。  同樣是民主黨成員，網民稱讚的通常是許智峯、鄺俊宇，狠批的主要則是黃碧雲，尹兆堅的存在感卻一直很低，即使多番在前線被捕及中椒，通常都很快被遺忘，討論區很少人談論他。尹說，朋友替他不值，他卻自問從政不是為了這些光環，「起碼我對得住自己」。"},{"pid":"f6d0d28f308fc206cadd40f4f6df6a3e881755e5","tid":2317264,"uid":212249,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/goodestchannel/video/5fce495d7220b700073e5854/反抗者們︱身負7條控罪拒絕流亡%20尹兆堅：絕不退出民主運動?fromSource=App\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel%2Fvideo%2F5fce495d7220b700073e5854%2F%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97%E8%80%85%E5%80%91%EF%B8%B1%E8%BA%AB%E8%B2%A07%E6%A2%9D%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%2520%E5%B0%B9%E5%85%86%E5%A0%85%EF%BC%9A%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%3FfromSource%3DApp&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3WwHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=c479c485\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel%2Fvideo%2F5fce495d7220b700073e5854%2F%E5%8F%8D%E6%8A%97%E8%80%85%E5%80%91%EF%B8%B1%E8%BA%AB%E8%B2%A07%E6%A2%9D%E6%8E%A7%E7%BD%AA%E6%8B%92%E7%B5%95%E6%B5%81%E4%BA%A1%2520%E5%B0%B9%E5%85%86%E5%A0%85%EF%BC%9A%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E9%80%80%E5%87%BA%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%81%8B%E5%8B%95%3FfromSource%3DApp&h=34afa0ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/goodestchannel/video/5fce495d7220b700073e5854/反抗者們︱身負7條控罪拒絕流亡%20尹兆堅：絕不退出民主運動?fromSource=App</a>"},{"pid":"483934c83e959abcd573d80f23368fbc422f370b","tid":2317264,"uid":91397,"li